title: Angels And Airwaves-We Dont Need To Whisper
description:
Angels and Airwaves (AVA) is a band that was formed by former Blink-182 and Box Car Racer guitarist/vocalist Tom DeLonge after he left Blink-182. The band includes the Over My Dead Body, Hazen Street and Box Car Racer guitarist David Kennedy, ex-Distillers bassist Ryan Sinn, and current Offspring drummer Atom Willard. AVA released their first single, "The Adventure", on May 18, 2006 and their debut album, We Don&#039;t Need to Whisper, on May 23, 2006.
